# Full Body Circuit [HIIT] @RPE 8
@ equipment: kettlebell, pull-up bar

> Rest 60s between exercises within each round.
> Scale pull-ups to ring rows if needed.

- Warmup 5min @Z1

- circuit 4x:
  @ rest_between_rounds: 90s
  - Kettlebell Swing 15rep @24kg
  - Push-Up 15rep
  - Goblet Squat 12rep @24kg
  - Pull-Up 8rep
  - Burpee 10rep
